description: SEED is an acronym for ‘SINO ECO ENERGY DEVELOPMENT'. Headquartered in Singapore, SEED is involved in eco-friendly energy development projects across the globe. SEED has created a completely new eco-friendly business platform based on blockchain where individuals can participate in eco-friendly energy development projects. Individuals can purchase SEED cryptocurrency to participate in an eco-friendly business and receive the harvests generated from the project under the same harvest rate as the institutional investors such as governments and investment banks. With this business platform, SEED hopes that everybody in the world can participate in the effort to save our planet and share harvests.
name: SEED
